reviewText: A huge DISSAPOINTMENT!  I READ THE DETAILS CAREFULLY AND STILL ORDERED THIS THINKING I WAS GOING TO GET A DVD FULL OF CARZY MOVIE TRAILERS. I GOT A DVD FULL OF CRAZY MOVIE TRAILERS....AUDIO ONLY!!!!! YEP! NO VISUALS AT ALL THESE ARE ALL MP3 SOUND FILES. THATS IT. OVER 8 HOURS OF THE SOUND OF CRAZY MOVIE TRAILERS. ONLY INSIDE DO YOU REALIZE THAT ITS AUDIO.
